## Requires

* pbkdf
* drbg
* ansi-terminal
* regex-posix

Try `cabal install ...` to get them.

## Storage file layout:

|salt     |verifier1|verifier2|representation of Storage data type|
|plaintext|encrypted                                              |

* length of salt: 16 bytes
* length of verifier1 and verifier2: 17 bytes

